snippet.title: Scamber Alert 🚨
snippet.description:
John Yates had several fraudulent  welfare check visit by the police AKA fraudulent emergency calls and swatting.  These police calls in video. All took place between June and the end of September.  In mid November and on December 25th 2021 two of the people who made these fraudulent calls were outed.  
 People on YouTube abuse the police and the emergency call systems far too much. This is an example of a few times that they were misused illegally. Yes, this is against the law.
 Thank you for watching.  Please comment below and Subscribe.
